set.name: Nager IT - The Fair Mouse
set.description: Nager IT was founded in 2009 with the goal to improve labour conditions in the globalised electronics production by giving a better practise: "the Fair Mouse". The current supply chain of our mouse is already 2/3 fair. And of course, we continue till we reach the 100%!
